#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a module to configure essential paths for the &plasma; desktop."
msgstr "To je modul za konfiguracijo bistvenih poti za namizje &plasma;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure some &kde; paths</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfigurirajte nekaj &kde; poti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure some &kde; paths</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfigurirajte nekaj &kde; poti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drives that are automounted at login cannot be used as paths. Such drives "
"will be reverted to defaults during restart of &plasma;."
msgstr ""
"Pogonov, ki so samodejno nameščeni ob prijavi, ni mogoče uporabiti kot poti. "
"Takšni pogoni bodo med ponovnim zagonom programa &plasma; povrnjeni na "
"privzete nastavitve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Desktop path:"
msgstr "Pot do namizja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Desktop folder contains all the files which you see in a "
"<guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> widget on your desktop. The default path is "
"usually <filename class=\"directory\">~/Desktop</filename> but you can "
"change here the location of this folder."
msgstr ""
"Mapa namizja vsebuje vse datoteke, ki so prikazane v gradniku "
"<guilabel>Pogled map</guilabel> na namizju. Privzeta pot je običajno "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/Desktop</filename>, vendar lahko tukaj "
"spremenite lokacijo te mape."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documents path:"
msgstr "Pot do dokumentov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This folder will be used by default to load or save documents from or to."
msgstr ""
"Ta mapa bo privzeto uporabljena za nalaganje ali shranjevanje dokumentov iz "
"ali v to mapo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Downloads path:"
msgstr "Pot do prenosov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "This folder will be used by default to save your downloaded items."
msgstr "Ta mapa bo privzeto uporabljena za shranjevanje prenesenih elementov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Videos path:"
msgstr "Pot do videoposnetkov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "This folder will be used by default to load or save movies from or to."
msgstr "Ta mapa bo privzeto uporabljena za nalaganje ali shranjevanje filmov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pictures path:"
msgstr "Pot do slik:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This folder will be used by default to load or save pictures from or to."
msgstr ""
"Ta mapa bo privzeto uporabljena za nalaganje ali shranjevanje slik iz ali v "
"to mapo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Music path:"
msgstr "Pot do glasbe:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "This folder will be used by default to load or save music from or to."
msgstr ""
"Ta mapa bo privzeto uporabljena za nalaganje ali shranjevanje glasbe iz nje "
"ali vanjo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you change a path and click <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> a dialog appears "
"where you can choose to move the content to the new folder or use the new "
"folder without moving the files."
msgstr ""
"Če spremenite pot in kliknete <guibutton>Potrdi</guibutton>, se prikaže "
"pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko izberete premik vsebine v novo mapo ali "
"uporabo nove mape brez premikanja datotek."
